Nemesis Enforcer:




Nemesis Enforcer saw Prowl crash.  Taking out his missile launcher, replacing 
the weapon of destruction with his simple rifle, he took aim, firing a rocket 
at the downed Prowl.  After he fired the rocket, he recieved Zardus' com 
transmission.  <Full retreat, got it!> he acknowledged, transforming to beast 
mode and heading towards the Alliance base.
